text: Food always super yums at this stall, and owners are friendly and nice!! Some of my favs so far are their pork banh mi, summer rolls, and pho. The best Viet food I've had so far, and it doesn't burn a hole in your wallet!

This stall is quiet and unassuming. Ordered the Grilled Chicken dry noodles and it was tasty. The best Vietnamese dry noodle I had! The sauce made it so refreshing for the hot weather. It also come with a spring roll which is nice as well. I had a fulfilling lunch. ðŸ˜‹

My favourite Vietnamese food, highly recommend the Banh Mi and summer roll

So far all the dishes have been a hit, the beef noodles and pork rice are worth a try!

The lady boss is also very friendly and kind, when we ate there she will serve the food to us which is so sweet.

Delicious and affordable food, good value for money. Love the summer rolls and chicken salad.

The Vietnamese lady is very friendly and speaks both English and Mandarin too. Supports cashless payment (paynow) and you can even order in advance via WhatsApp.

Able to pre order via their whatsapp number - 86680344!

Ordered 2 items:
B5 Grilled Pork w vermicelli - grilled pork taste and smell very fragrant. the peanuts & fried onions adds a nice aroma and crunch to the dish

B12 Fresh Summer Rolls - nice! lettuce and cucumber are fresh. the rolls are wrapped in plastic to ensure the rolls do not stick together.
